Responsibilities & Requirements:


Handle air-conditioning maintenance in data centre for our clients;
Minimum 2 years’ solid experience in air-conditioning;
Knowledge in CRAC/Chiller system is preferable;
Good communication skills, customer-oriented;
Candidate with data centre experience will be an advantage;
Candidate with more experience will be considered as Senior Technician/Assistant Supervisor
職責及資歷:

負責數據中心外勤保養及維修冷氣系統;
具備最少2年冷氣保養及維修或相關經驗;
懂CRAC與中央冷水機系統優先考慮;
良好溝通及顧客服務技巧;
有數據中心維修服務經驗者更佳;
較多經驗者將會考慮為高級技術員或助理主管
有花紅, 牙科福利, 醫療保險, 超時工作津貼, 晉升機會及進修津貼, 上班時間上午9時至下午6時, 每週工作6天, 每天工作 8 小時, 享有公衆假期; 


An attractive remuneration package and fringe benefit will be offered to the right candidate. Interested parties, please send your resume stating with current and expected salary to the Human Resources Department by clicking Apply Now.

For more information, please visit the corporate website at http://www.newtechapac.com

 All information received will be kept confidential and for recruitment purposes only. Response will only be given to short-listed candidates.

